name: My Childhood Universe
description:
Childhood is very fun, we are free to do whatever we like, when our day starts with cartoons and ends with playing.

This is the last episode of the first series.

The previous episode was the imagination of Beansboyz and his younger sister playing in his room, everything he did from being chased by monsters, monsters destroying the city to the arrival of the hero who saved the city.

A child's imagination has no limits, it all comes from his love and affection for something fun to play with.

Welcome to the childhood Universe of beansboyz and friends.
